FBIS3-6172 "dreas050_q_94001" FBIS-EAS-94-050 Document Type:Daily Report 15 Mar 1994 AUSTRALASIA Australia Navy Seizes Indonesian Boat for Illegal Fishing BK1503080794 Melbourne Radio Australia in English 0500 GMT 15 Mar 94 BK1503080794 Melbourne Radio Australia Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] An Indonesian fishing boat has been apprehended by the Australian Navy near Christmas Island in the Indian Ocean. The boat with 13 crew was spotted near the island yesterday by the Broome-based coast watch aircraft. It is alleged the longline vessel was fishing illegally in Australian waters. The vessel is being escorted by the Navy patrol boat Gawler and it is expected to reach Christmas Island later today.
